Polonaises, and
two lovely piano concertos.

28
00:01:57.150 --> 00:02:03.490
Our aim with Chopin, will be to focus on
the Nocturne genre that he made famous.

29
00:02:03.490 --> 00:02:04.520
What's a Nocturne?

30
00:02:04.520 --> 00:02:08.230
Well as the name suggests it's a night
piece, but a dreamy night piece.

31
00:02:08.230 --> 00:02:13.080
